    <item>
      <title>如果格雷厄姆·普拉特纳退出缅因州参议员竞选，谁可能取代他？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/who-would-replace-graham-platner-maine.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果格雷厄姆·普拉特纳在下周退出，他可以在选票上被替换。如果他这样做，缅因州民主党将面临一场不确定的两周竞选来选择继任者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/who-would-replace-graham-platner-maine.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 22:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
